Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.00,0:22:30.92,Ending - RO,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.3}nani ga attemo zutto hanaranaide kureta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:30.92,Ending - ENG,,0,0,0,,But no matter what, you always stay by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:37.09,Ending - RO,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.3\c&H000000&}dareka wo mamorinuku to dareka ni tsumi wo tsukuru
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.92,0:22:37.09,Ending - RO,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.3}dareka wo mamorinuku to dareka ni tsumi wo tsukuru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:37.09,Ending - ENG,,0,0,0,,By protecting someone, you create a sin for someone else.
