Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.69,0:23:01.82,Ending - RO,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.3}kimi no sonzai dake de sekai wa mangekyou mitai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:23:01.82,Ending - ENG,,0,0,0,,With just your presence, the world begins to look like a kaleidoscope.
